cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with pose estimation of objects in a single RGB image using deep learning methods. 
2. cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the proposed method can be applied in industrial automation and robotics. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper utilizes a convolutional neural network for object detection. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a likely category as the paper proposes an approach to generate datasets and label them automatically. 
5. cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper uses CAD models for pose estimation.
